{"tid":130044,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布火影係皇道漫畫世界第一","createTime":"2017-02-22T05:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T04:12:49.000Z","uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b81a09a2ded79bf433b295ecd3b996ea5aa59c","tid":130044,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"咁火影緊係聽唔到魔法戰爭至高指令嘅引擎聲啦。兩個level我都費事比到火影變辣殺。<br />\n<br />\n之旦係之旦係，火影忍者皇道漫畫世界第一係冇得駁嘅。拎MK最愛嘅巨人一拳比，比完應該大家都同意我嘅講法。<br />\n<br />\n先講巨人，巨人咁多人話正，話佢好撚政治，講緊香港（你唔好撚傻啦，我估作者連地球有到叫香港都唔知呀。）火影就唔同，我好撚肯定作者寫緊香港！先唔講岸本應該黎過香港簽名（應該有？），所以一定知地球有香港；更重要嘅火影提到嘅係，話撚知你係天才定努力，你冇父幹通通都收皮！同香港一樣呀！你老豆冇塞隻尾獸（樓）比你，港女櫻眼尾都唔會望你一下（你係MK 都仲有啲用嘅），你幾努力考會考讀大學，讀到開埋八門訓埋醫院都係冇用。最最最重要係有父幹最尾可以食大波妹！呢個有啲問題，香港冇大波妹，不過作者日本人我唔怪佢。講香港，巨人？不了。火影先係！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一套一拳，打得爽？火影最尾個撚個大炮元氣玉亂扔仲爽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我宣布火影忍者皇道漫畫世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有麻煩大家睇下魔法戰爭，睇完先知咩係真神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bc079c3d0a1cbb93161be8e0fde6d3d1a875ae","tid":130044,"uid":67461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:51:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba2b7805beaec17be2e7621e84b953366d3521dc","tid":130044,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"你個名，有兩個世界第一，邊個先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9267ba1135bbe08158e9fed286fc28db4ace2f","tid":130044,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個名，有兩個世界第一，邊個先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都話左火影只係皇道漫畫世界第一"},{"pid":"84d5e51016135d5d8e03b20f2931d65326fa5624","tid":130044,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:26:32.000Z","msg":"已經冇咩好笑"},{"pid":"30c49e4f10d9605057e2e77e1d9f06f05831e178","tid":130044,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"大大聲話我聽 龍珠 JOJO 係乜?"},{"pid":"7438dfa48c13d0c483029bc4985f1cc1da24de30","tid":130044,"uid":34929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"一拳幾時變左mk最愛"},{"pid":"2838be9a660857ede2cea93b122ad39ddc7e9d70","tid":130044,"uid":46717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"粉俠傳先係"},{"pid":"dcaa5805f9de2c9855b25cf1ff3083e7dff2dc84","tid":130044,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>粉俠傳先係</blockquote><br />\n呢個駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff07de5278a40de7786e522609369ab2edb9354","tid":130044,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大大聲話我聽 龍珠 JOJO 係乜?</blockquote><br />\n唔入流啦，一個打鬥冇腦，一個故事多bug <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b747906771a67caea318b537d386e7f67c6f47a","tid":130044,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大大聲話我聽 龍珠 JOJO 係乜?</blockquote><br />\n唔入流啦，一個打鬥冇腦，一個故事多bug <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個兩隻垃圾啦 龍珠個主角成個弱智仔咁 你去龍珠post都大把人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\njojo唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b001812e774678aa5507e36d421a6555369602","tid":130044,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"一個主角可以咁多外掛係身 打垃圾輕鬆一波車埋人地到啦 <br />\n唔夠揪就開嘴遁屈返人機<br />\n咁都唔叫皇道叫咩 最皇道嘅動漫一定係火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e565adcdefca6801ac4eb581aabdb07f8ed5e3","tid":130044,"uid":8307,"like":0,"d